name: Star%27s_Delight_pilot
content: A Sullustan female served as pilot of the Gymsnor-3 light freighter Star's Delight under Captain Lai Nootka. When the Star's Delight was impounded by Imperial authorities while delivering X-wing parts and proton torpedoes to Garqi, the Sullustan was taken prisoner along with the rest of the crew. They were rescued by a group of students led by Dynba Tesc in a plan devised by former Corellian Security Force officer Corran Horn, and escaped the planet aboard the Star's Delight.
